name: Honey, Please Say Something Before You Leave Me
description:
Listen to the official audio of Boo Morrison's "Honey, Please Say Something Before You Leave Me ft. Zoom Sonsakun, Frong Siwakorn, benz evans" from the EP "BIRTH OF A SCUMBAG"

Lyrics : Patipan Worawan IG :@boobluesman
Vocals : Patipan Worawan IG :@boobluesman

Bass : Maytasit Nitiwattanapong IG :@maytarsit.k
Produced : Wacharakorn Suwancharoen IG :@benzevans._
Mixed and Mastered : Wacharakorn Suwancharoen IG :@benzevans._ 
Album Cover Design : Prasobchai Suklert IG :@mister.pschsl

Lyrics
Well, what a long day 
I'm so sick and tried of feeling this way
When the sun goes down, I can't lay down
And when the sun has risen, I'm feeling down
Because living without you is the hardest thing I've ever had to do
How am I supposed to live without you?
Honey, honey
Please, say something before you leave, girl

Well, honey
I've told you remember?
